{"TopicId":149010,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Simple Questions","CreatedByName":"The Space Dino","CreatedById":163476,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-30T13:08:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"The Space Dino","CreatedById":163476,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-30T13:08:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs said in the title above, I have a 2\u00A0simple questions to ask:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1) How do you put a signature?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2) How do you post pictures without imgur?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DrLicor","CreatedById":165712,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-30T13:29:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey, me again \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Go to you profile -\u0026gt; you get a little screen with:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E- Content\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProfile\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E- Settings\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E...\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0026gt;Account settings.\u0026lt;\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClick on account setting -\u0026gt; from there you can click on signature and change it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. you can\u0027t post them without an internetlink. You have to post them on a site like imgur... (as far as I\u00A0know)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-top:0px;color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022margin-top:0px;color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\nso make an account on imgur,\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://imgur.com/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022color:rgb(60,105,148);text-decoration:underline;background-color:transparent;\u0022\u003Ehttp://imgur.com/,\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003Efrom there on your can drop you images on the internet, since the forum/pm-chat needs a image from an URL. To drop an image on imgur, just click on new post (next to the logo on the top left and you need to be logged in).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\nSo thats how to drop an image on the internet, click on you account in imgur -\u0026gt; images -\u0026gt; then select the desired image you want to share with me (one at a time), when you click on that, imgur opens your image and on the right there will be some links, copy the\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong style=\u0022font-weight:bold;\u0022\u003EDirect Link.\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003EThis will be something like\u00A0\u0027\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/OVG0XXB.jpg\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022color:rgb(60,105,148);text-decoration:underline;background-color:transparent;\u0022\u003Ehttp://i.imgur.com/OVG0XXB.jpg\u003C/a\u003E\u0027\u00A0this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\nYou can than paste the link in your text here or just click on \u0027insert other media\u0027 -\u0026gt; \u0027insert image from URL\u0027\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022color:rgb(39,42,52);font-family:\u0027Helvetica Neue\u0027, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-30T13:30:49Z\u0022 title=\u002209/30/2016 01:30  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 30, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by DrLicor\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-30T14:20:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved over to the Kerbal Network, as it\u0027s about the forum and not the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1) See \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/165712-drlicor/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022165712\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/165712-drlicor/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@DrLicor\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s answer. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2) They need to be hosted somewhere, imgur is popular but not necessary. I use dropbox personally, there are many other choices. To embed the picture, get the URL of the image itself (should end in .jpg,\u00A0.png, or .gif or whatever file type), paste it into the post and the forum software will create the embed automagically.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Space Dino","CreatedById":163476,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-01T07:45:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222781111\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022149010\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221475245211\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2) They need to be hosted somewhere, imgur is popular but not necessary. I use dropbox personally, there are many other choices. To embed the picture, get the URL of the image itself (should end in .jpg,\u00A0.png, or .gif or whatever file type), paste it into the post and the forum software will create the embed automagically.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you get the URL of the picture?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DrLicor","CreatedById":165712,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-01T08:12:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor imgur, see my post above, for Dropbox, rightclick on the picture you like to share, when in your dropboxfolder, and click copy link or share link, not sure.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-10-01T08:15:50Z\u0022 title=\u002210/01/2016 08:15  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 1, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by DrLicor\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Space Dino","CreatedById":163476,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-10-02T01:01:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk, thanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}